  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Safeguarding in Faith Communities",
  "purpose": "To focus on safeguarding concerns relevant to any community of faith, belief or religion. The APPG attempts to raise awareness and improve policy and practice in relation to safeguarding in faith communities and by encouraging both the opportunity and responsibility of those faith groups and communities in creating safer places for all.",
